Articles.Title: How They Made Harrison Ford Look 40 Years Younger in 'Indiana Jones and the Dial of Destiny'
Articles.Description: In the the fifth Indiana Jones movie, viewers got brand-new footage of 39-year-old Indy — though actor Harrison Ford is 81. Allure spoke with visual effects artists who pulled off the de-aging process to find out exactly how they did it.
